This page tabulates the numeric IDs for each key in ''Java Edition'' 1.12.2, before keys were given dedicated alphanumeric IDs in 17w43a and beyond. These numbers can be found by opening options.txt in a text editor.

Display names which are left blank appear blank in-game.
